Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.84,0:00:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷歐帕羅特把跳躍坐標設定在Kirkwood了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.75,0:00:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.34,0:00:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽得到吧 雷歐帕羅特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.65,0:00:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是對即將君臨宇宙的王者該用的口氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.23,0:00:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷歐帕羅特？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.64,0:00:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受我的支配 為了我努力工作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.83,0:00:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們都做了什麼突擊工事啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.22,0:00:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了那是妖刀了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.13,0:00:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量供給太陽能鏡全部被雷歐帕羅特破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.70,0:00:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新市民收容區域處於非常危險的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.78,0:00:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就去 打倒雷歐帕羅特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.52,0:00:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我的太陽能鏡提供電力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.74,0:00:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.52,0:00:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷歐帕羅特真的做了這種事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.89,0:00:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是他的本來面目
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.55,0:00:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就待在這裡 比任何地方都安全
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.25,0:00:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底誰是好人誰是壞人呢 我已經不明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.65,0:00:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have control
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.72,0:01:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定要做個了斷 雷歐帕羅特
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.70,0:01:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我已經不再需要你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.55,0:01:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來讓你把惡作劇做的有點過分了呢 雷歐帕羅特
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.28,0:01:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是……
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.19,0:01:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你這個樣子 我還遠不能把世界交你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.05,0:01:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兒子喲！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.58,0:01:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 妹子在…那裡面…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.56,0:01:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.68,0:01:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居民的避難已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 秋葉！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.07,0:03:10.15,EDTITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(450,290)}{\fs45}{\fad(500,500)}諸神的黃昏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓這個世界充滿憎惡 矗立於漆黑的頂點的就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得這不像是雷歐帕羅特了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.05,0:03:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的本質覺醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.22,0:03:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到為了保護我的世界而製作出來的你 會對我露出獠牙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.35,0:03:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.20,0:03:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不接受任何人的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.93,0:03:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷歐帕羅特在動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.90,0:03:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 快點到地下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.15,0:03:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請快點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.84,0:03:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神……有我一個就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.09,0:03:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我不起作用的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.68,0:04:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這……這是……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.25,0:04:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為碎藻吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎怎怎 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.13,0:04:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋葉 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.48,0:04:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去救妹子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.72,0:04:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事嗎 Nerval先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.43,0:04:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強大的神 要去打倒更強大的神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.74,0:04:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我教導給兒子的生存原理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.12,0:04:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多麼諷刺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經不能動了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.77,0:04:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的首級 我取下了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.96,0:04:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快讓我們乘上去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.19,0:04:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你 就算只有這孩子能上…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.16,0:04:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋葉 現在不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:04:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不去 妹子就……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋葉 稍微考慮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.93,0:05:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋葉！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.01,0:05:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請排成4列
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.38,0:05:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋葉……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.20,0:05:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊月
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神風
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.01,0:05:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 你又要逃？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.87,0:05:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.53,0:05:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋葉 你又亂來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.22,0:05:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊月
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.68,0:05:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋葉 這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.97,0:05:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.66,0:05:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果和50年前的構造一樣的話 Nerval就在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概 妹子也在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.67,0:05:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子…就在這
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 秋葉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.22,0:05:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去 秋葉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.14,0:06:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易做好了打倒Nerval的準備 現在一切都糟蹋了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.65,0:06:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我們要怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.27,0:06:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們又要到處流浪了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別恐慌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之現在先確保安全 按順序處理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.16,0:06:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中樞單元嚴重毀壞 身體不受控制
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊 就這點而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.08,0:06:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭腦房？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.93,0:06:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.66,0:06:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.07,0:06:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是妹子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.47,0:06:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.77,0:06:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋葉大小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.11,0:06:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫出
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.76,0:07:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐 請快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.78,0:07:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.88,0:07:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.15,0:07:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然丟下這不管 呆子！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.56,0:07:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界又將改變
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 Existent-Z！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.77,0:07:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈美 是奈美嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.07,0:07:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.40,0:07:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你會是第一個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.78,0:08:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 算是從最弱的傢伙開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將姐姐們一個個解決掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.97,0:08:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將獅子堂家毀滅掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呢 奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是為了戰鬥而來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說著「打倒Nerval 保護人類」什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.38,0:08:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是來接妹子的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.97,0:08:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的我才不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.59,0:08:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.79,0:08:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是……太不中用了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.02,0:08:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讓我很不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我快來！Existent-Z！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Existent-Z？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.93,0:08:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗乃香？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別搗亂 我想快點找到妹子 救她出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.80,0:09:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才管那種事 把大家都毀滅就行了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.93,0:09:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒空理你！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.20,0:09:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是對親人該說的話？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.32,0:09:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙全體都在戰鬥的時候 你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子 妹子的 只為自己考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.06,0:09:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你算哪門子「穿越宇宙的少女」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.86,0:09:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你穿越什麼宇宙了 你什麼都沒穿越！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.79,0:09:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明什麼都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.63,0:09:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼比起我 你這種傢伙更受人溺愛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.76,0:09:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了 你們這些呆機械！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事 Nerval大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:10:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢 和煮芋頭一起到哪風流去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.42,0:10:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個蘿莉控變態機械傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.10,0:10:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算背叛我們嗎 奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.57,0:10:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒成灰吧 鐵皮女！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.51,0:10:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂被…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.48,0:10:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋葉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.93,0:10:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊月 穗乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真吵啊 這些傢伙也是 一切都是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.10,0:10:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.89,0:10:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來制止我看下啊 秋葉！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈美！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.08,0:10:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都給我毀滅吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.02,0:10:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈美！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.15,0:11:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈美 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.23,0:11:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還敢問我？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然真的朝自己妹妹開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.98,0:11:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要拋棄我到什麼程度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.63,0:11:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.59,0:11:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋葉！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.56,0:11:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E……Existent-Z
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.40,0:12:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護對像搞錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.64,0:12:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那傢伙給我撕成八塊啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.99,0:12:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的 奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Existent-Z本來就是那孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.97,0:12:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿越宇宙的少女的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.26,0:12:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什……麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧 全都去死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.42,0:12:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈美！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.57,0:12:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讓人頭疼的孩子 到底是誰教育她的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.58,0:12:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是小秋葉吧 好啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.14,0:12:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇到你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.09,0:12:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為太突然了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.90,0:12:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.18,0:12:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.63,0:12:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是神樂……嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.61,0:12:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗乃香 讓你擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:12:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.39,0:13:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.60,0:13:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.24,0:13:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.04,0:13:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你恢復原樣了 神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.53,0:13:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是懷有夢想的 一天的日子 救護車！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.68,0:13:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經把你修好了 你能別扯那種破嗓子了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真失禮呢 這是很合人類的好歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.90,0:13:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶 評議會的聯絡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有 會長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.30,0:13:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在雷歐帕羅特那發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 好像有什麼東西漂流過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是個髒西西的巨大垃圾似的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.27,0:13:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杜鵑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.27,0:13:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這樣說對死人不太尊敬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.57,0:13:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你傢伙還真是到最後都沒能得到好報啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.88,0:13:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你說的話我完全摸不著邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.20,0:14:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別隨便發我便當！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.26,0:14:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詐……詐屍了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.60,0:14:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你笨蛋嗎 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.41,0:14:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杜……杜鵑……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經厭倦爭紛了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.87,0:14:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只會讓人失去重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.47,0:14:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 會陷入憎恨的連鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.56,0:14:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就此隱居……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弁慶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.20,0:14:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好想想 我們會落到如此境地是因為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.23,0:14:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,造成這種慘狀的原因是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那……那是因為……就是說……爭紛的……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.41,0:14:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不是神之旨意或者大宇宙的意識什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雷歐帕羅特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣！那個雷歐帕羅特就是一切的元兇！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.99,0:14:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被打了就要打回去 弁慶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.29,0:14:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢朝我的帝國放箭的那個混蛋竹輪！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.97,0:14:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把他切成圓片 放到太陽裡除去水分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.40,0:15:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再像炸甜甜圈那樣把他給炸個香噴噴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.20,0:15:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸成黃褐色！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杜鵑？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為太餓所以心情不好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 小弁慶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.49,0:15:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊月 是往這邊走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.33,0:15:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 ICP的誘導信號確實是從這邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.19,0:15:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.02,0:15:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.84,0:15:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等等 秋葉是……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.93,0:15:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是同罪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗噗 活該
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.07,0:15:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被訓斥了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們沒好好看守也有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道自己在做什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.66,0:15:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果現在在打仗的話 會被當做臨陣脫逃處刑的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:15:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別用那種口氣說話啊 我只是……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.96,0:15:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該理解了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.28,0:16:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要整頓事態 你就必須作為作戰的核心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.35,0:16:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為我是「穿越宇宙的少女」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐才是 該適可而止了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.04,0:16:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自把那種名號加到我頭上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.11,0:16:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那是什麼啊 「穿越宇宙的少女」什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.33,0:16:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Existent-Z的女王 擁有黃金槍的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.08,0:16:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為人工智能殖民地之間的戰鬥劃上休止符
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.76,0:16:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是「穿越宇宙的少女」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.34,0:16:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神……神樂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.27,0:16:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 她是阿蕾達 只是裝作神樂大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 她已經恢復了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.84,0:16:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們所熟悉的神樂又回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.24,0:16:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結結實實地吃到了奈美的Anti-QT呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.40,0:16:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢復到本來面目了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.54,0:16:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遺憾 我還想讓你們多頭疼一陣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.39,0:16:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種……和氣氛不符的玩笑是……
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼那位大人是……
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賀統 矢藏 風魔 馮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.79,0:16:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼長時間 大家忍受過來真辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.73,0:17:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我們又這樣集合在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.92,0:17:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個Nerval最畏懼的Enigma同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.86,0:17:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您真是神樂大人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前進吧 戰鬥還沒終止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.99,0:17:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.07,0:17:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小秋葉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.95,0:17:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是最後的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作為「穿越宇宙的少女」沒能讓戰鬥結束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.33,0:17:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你一定能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼承了我的願望的你一定能…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.39,0:17:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個小姐是最後的王牌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.67,0:17:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就知道秋葉不是簡單的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從以前開始 就是那樣忽悠別人去工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.77,0:17:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 確實是神樂大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.03,0:17:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請下令 秋葉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.99,0:17:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正是為了這個瞬間而誕生的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.33,0:17:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了終結戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:17:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也助你一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.43,0:18:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不會讓神風一個人耍帥的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.00,0:18:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人工智能殖民地什麼的只需"Fu~"的一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.37,0:18:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等……等等 等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.58,0:18:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會試試看的 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.54,0:18:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了 秋葉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.74,0:18:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是只有你才能完成的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.60,0:18:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺掉雷歐帕羅特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.38,0:18:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個……不是Nerval？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.82,0:18:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況改變了 你也明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要殺的是雷歐帕羅特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.20,0:18:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.47,0:18:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於被雷歐帕羅特破壞了太陽鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.19,0:18:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kirkwood全域的生命維持機能顯著下降了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不殺雷歐帕羅特 Kirkwood就會被毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.77,0:18:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.42,0:18:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡到底是……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.30,0:18:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的中樞部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.58,0:18:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記錄著所有構造體與人類的歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.42,0:19:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣 又能重新開始新的循環
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在美好中循環著的完整的人類社會 實現人類終極的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.51,0:19:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是我的自我實現
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.40,0:19:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要給予舒適的空間以及該做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.95,0:19:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類就會安定並且滿足
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.54,0:19:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過奈美這個素材 我確信了這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這……這不是……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.80,0:19:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enigma嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.64,0:19:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 燒成灰燼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈美幹的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.46,0:19:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 她在想什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.01,0:19:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種無聊的世界 真想把一切都毀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:19:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是渴望破壞之人麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:20:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色的……神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報上名來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.02,0:20:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿越宇宙的少女·Black
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.32,0:20:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.15,0:20:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來我身邊吧 少女·Black
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.29,0:20:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.76,0:20:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你算哪門子「穿越宇宙的少女」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.73,0:20:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都做不到的你！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈美說的對 我什麼都……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.65,0:20:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在這裡止步不前了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.11,0:20:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不可能的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.88,0:20:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只有你才能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.57,0:20:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣說也……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦才好呢 妹子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.92,0:20:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐 請快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.25,0:20:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.06,0:20:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事的……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.53,0:20:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是那種時候 也在擔心我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.50,0:20:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我……在看著妹子的什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.53,0:21:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子一直想著保護我 保護大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.05,0:21:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我……一直在依靠著妹子 一直被保護著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.79,0:21:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.25,0:21:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不就和奈美說的一樣 什麼也做不了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.76,0:21:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須上了  這是只有我才能做到的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.27,0:21:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 我要做！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.06,0:21:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經下定決議了呢 秋葉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.57,0:21:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也一起戰鬥！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.83,0:21:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.78,0:21:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.86,0:21:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得找到並阻止奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.28,0:21:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈美？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.54,0:21:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我把她牽扯進來的 我有責任
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.52,0:21:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 不阻止她的話 那孩子會死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.08,0:21:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.58,0:21:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 愚民們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.99,0:21:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.87,0:21:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 黑暗的統治者 黑暗王子大人要進行肅清了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.92,0:21:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啪！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.92,0:22:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獅子堂島……在燃燒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.77,0:22:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒吧燒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.57,0:22:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是哪兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.90,0:24:14.90,EDTITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(455,310)}足下的宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.81,0:24:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終回的暗示
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.26,0:24:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最壯大的情節
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.81,0:24:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,shuu~
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.46,0:24:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎來完結的電視劇
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.99,0:24:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,kai~ kai kai?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.02,0:24:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋葉！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.64,0:24:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這最後的預告了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.18,0:24:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,kai kai……
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.97,0:24:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪獸大攻擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.39,0:01:38.49,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡はいつでもそばにある
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.51,0:01:48.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輝きたいよ　未来へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.48,0:02:04.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたの中　騒めくノイズは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.48,0:02:12.05,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馴れ愛の束縛　動けない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.93,0:02:18.87,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦しみが散らばる世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.90,0:02:24.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探して　失い、また求めて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.97,0:02:30.05,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辿って　わたしの糸を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:34.06,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡は必然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.10,0:02:41.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そっと抱いてあげる　一雫の痛みも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.91,0:02:47.86,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯った証が　星になる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:54.24,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扉をあけて　飛べるよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.39,0:01:38.49,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡一直就在我們身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.51,0:01:48.47,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們想要發光 照亮未來…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.48,0:02:04.43,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你心中的 凌亂的雜音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.48,0:02:12.05,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是已熟知的愛的束縛 …動彈不得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.93,0:02:18.87,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦遍佈著這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.90,0:02:24.10,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋找著… 失去，然後再次追求
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.97,0:02:30.05,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追溯吧 沿著我的軌跡…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:34.06,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡必然會發生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.10,0:02:41.90,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄地將你抱住 不讓你有一點疼痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.91,0:02:47.86,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點亮的證明 成為了恆星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:54.24,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開門扉吧… 飛向天空！

Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.47,0:22:45.70,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甦る痛みに流されながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.71,0:22:54.58,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷徨って僕らはどこへ行くんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.60,0:23:08.89,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懐かしく暖かな空　その眩しい景色へ描いた幻は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.90,0:23:15.54,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揺れて消えた　遠く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.95,0:23:25.15,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解けぬ孤独を抱きながら　それでも祈ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.18,0:23:33.78,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰が同じ　希望の訪れが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.86,0:23:41.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闇の破片が　絶えず僕の　胸に突き刺さる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.15,0:23:51.04,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君という光　ただ　知りたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.47,0:22:45.70,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在甦醒的痛苦中隨波逐流
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.71,0:22:54.58,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷徨的我們不知要去往何方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.60,0:23:08.89,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那令人懷念地溫暖地天空 那種炫目地景色描繪出來的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.90,0:23:15.54,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搖擺不定地消失 在遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.95,0:23:25.15,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使被無法擺脫的孤獨抱住 我們也要祈禱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.18,0:23:33.78,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都一樣 希望總會到來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.86,0:23:41.13,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗的碎片 無休止地 刺向我的胸口
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.15,0:23:51.04,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想瞭解以你為名的光芒
